dist/
.astro/

# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Generated API reference (produced by `dotnet docfx metadata` + scripts/postprocess-api.mjs).
# index.md is a committed fallback so the /api/ route exists in content-only builds;
# postprocess-api.mjs overwrites it with the full namespace listing during CI deploys.
src/content/docs/api/*
!src/content/docs/api/index.md
src/generated/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
